Brazil Offers Cancer Treatment to Venezuela’s Chavez, Folha Says

-- B y   H a r r y   M a u r e r
-- 
2011-07-06T15:46:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/brazil-offers-cancer-treatment-to-venezuela-s-chavez-folha-says.html
Brazil ’s government has offered
cancer  treatment  to Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez , newspaper
Folha de S. Paulo reported, without saying where it obtained the
information.  The treatment would be offered within Brazil’s private
health-care system and the costs would be paid by  Venezuela ,
according to the Sao Paulo-based newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Harry Maurer in  Rio de Janeiro  at 
 hmaurer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
